citation: Proclamation under the Electricity Supply Industry Amendment Act 2003 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Electricity Supply Industry Amendment Act 2003

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Electricity Supply Industry Amendment Act 2003 fix 3 August 2005 as the day on which sections 34, 38, 40 and 41 of that Act commence.

25 July 2005

W. J. E. COX

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

P. A. LENNON

Treasurer

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 3 August 2005

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Treasury and Finance.
